description: This file defines a mock class `CloudStoreImplementationMock` for unit testing purposes. It inherits from multiple interfaces related to store operations such as IStore, IStore2, IStoreCache, IStoreInspector, and IStoreLimit, and uses Google Mock (`<gmock/gmock.h>`) to mock the methods of these interfaces.
